      "span_text": "We converted the relative ratio value for each BAC clones in each sample to score of 1 (gain/amplified), 0 (no change), or À1 (loss) based on the 2 s.d. standards described above and analyzed with Cluster and TreeView) (Cluster and TreeView software) based on the average linkage method with the centered correlation metric was used (or Pearson Uncentered)."
